<!-- The Water Crisis -->
<section class="py-14">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900">Understanding the Water Crisis</h2>
    <p class="mt-3 text-slate-700">
      Freshwater is finite and unevenly distributed. Growing demand, climate change, and pollution
      intensify scarcity. Conserving water protects ecosystems, communities, and future generations.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-8 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <!-- Card 1 -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow ring-1 ring-slate-200">
        <div class="text-3xl">🌍</div>
        <h3 class="mt-2 font-semibold">Global Challenge</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">
          Billions face unreliable access to clean water; local actions compound into global impact.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2 -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow ring-1 ring-slate-200">
        <div class="text-3xl">🔥</div>
        <h3 class="mt-2 font-semibold">Climate Pressure</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">
          Droughts, floods, and heat amplify stress on rivers, reservoirs, and groundwater.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3 -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 shadow ring-1 ring-slate-200">
        <div class="text-3xl">🧪</div>
        <h3 class="mt-2 font-semibold">Quality Matters</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">
          Contamination and leakage waste precious resources and increase treatment costs.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

