          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-2xl">✅</span>
            <span>Lower utility costs and reduce waste at source.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-2xl">✅</span>
            <span>Protect ecosystems and biodiversity dependent on base flows.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-2xl">✅</span>
            <span>Build resilience to droughts and climate volatility.</span>
          </li>
